          <h2>Bio (Award-Committee Ready)</h2>
          <p>
            Robert Simpson operates at the intersection of performance coaching and program architecture. His work is defined by structure: clear player pathways, measurable training standards, and scalable systems that elevate both individual development and community participation.
          </p>

          <ul class="bullets">
            <li><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span><div><b>PGA Professional</b> with a modern, performance-based coaching approach focused on long-term athlete development and transferable skill acquisition.</div></li>
