            <li><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span><div><b>Youth academy architect</b> designing structured junior progression: foundation, development, competitive readiness, and high performance.</div></li>
            <li><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span><div><b>Adult player development framework</b> built around scoring strategy, ball flight control, and practice models designed for on-course transfer.</div></li>
            <li><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span><div><b>Measurable results focus</b> using benchmarks, skill testing, progress reviews, and training blocks to drive consistent improvement.</div></li>
            <li><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span><div><b>Commitment to growth</b> through community programming and school partnerships that create access while maintaining high standards.</div></li>
